&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge Pre-Sales to Delivery:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the transition from sales to implementation, including scoping, SOW creation, and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as a Strategic Technical Advisor:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide customers on architecture decisions, best practices, and long-term scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Identify Expansion Opportunities:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with customers to uncover additional use cases and drive continued adoption and growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Close the Product Feedback Loop:&lt;/strong&gt; Surface recurring challenges and contribute to product improvements through technical insights and specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operate with Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage multiple high-impact projects simultaneously, maintaining a high bar for quality and execution&lt;/li&gt;
