&lt;p&gt;They are also highly manual and fragmented, deeply dependent on data quality&amp;nbsp; and lineage, and increasingly in need of &lt;strong&gt;AI-driven automation and insight generation&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager who operates as a builder and owner&lt;/strong&gt;, and who brings &lt;strong&gt;strong intuition for structured finance workflows&lt;/strong&gt;, to help define how these processes evolve in an AI-native world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own a product area end-to-end and shape how financial institutions go from &lt;strong&gt;raw financial data → models → insights → decisions → actions&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
